data.description: Nice place to call home in a quiet neighborhood. 4 bedrooms 2 bath home on approximately 1 acre. The 4th bedroom can be the perfect office with double doors. Small shed/workshop in the backyard. Plenty of room for horses/animals or recreational toys etc. Ramp in front for easy access to the house. Lots of cabinets in the kitchen along with an island. Water well inside a separate shed/pump house for protection from weather. Nice carport alongside the house. The driveway has two drive through gates.
